quran[13{c,v,t}:
19,52,hum ne uss ko tor ke dahni janib se puraka aur raaz ki guftagu se is ko taqarab ataa kya
19,53,aur apni meharbani se is ke bhai haroon ko nabi bana kar ussay ( madad gaar ke tor par ) diya
19,54,aur is kitaab mein Ismael ka zikar karo woh waday ka sacha tha aur rasool nabi tha
19,55,woh apne ghar walon ko namaz aur zkoh ka hukum deta tha aur apne rab ke nazdeek aik pasandeeda ensaan tha
19,56,aur is kitaab mein Adrees ka zikar karo woh aikrasbaaz ensaan aur aik nabi tha
19,57,aur usay hum ne buland maqam par uthaya tha
19,58,"yeh woh paighambar hain jin par Allah ne inaam farmaya aadam ki aulaad mein se, aur unn logon ki nasal se jinhein hum ne Nooh ke sath kashti par sawaar kya tha, a war ibrahim ki nasal se aur Israel ki nasal se aur yeh un logon mein se thay jin ko hum ne hadaayat bakhsh aur bargzida kya un ka haal yeh tha ke jab Rehman ki ayaat un ko sunai jatein to rotay hue sjday mein gir jatay thay"
19,59,"phir un ke baad woh nakhlf log un ke janasheen hue jinhon ne namaz ko zaya kya aur khwahisaat nafs ki pairwi ki, pas qareeb hai ke woh gumraahi ke injaam se dochar hon"
19,60,Albata jo tauba kar len aur imaan le ayen aur naik amli ikhtiyar kar len woh jannat mein daakhil hon ge aur un ki zarraa barabar haq talfi nah ho gi
19,61,un ke liye hamesha rehne wali jannaten hain jin ka Rehman ne apne bundon se Dur parda wada kar rakha hai aur yaqeenan yeh wada poora ho kar rehna hai
19,62,"wahan woh koi be Hooda baat nah sُnin ge, jo kuch bhi sُnin ge theek hi sunen ge aur un ka rizaq inhen pihm subah o shaam milta rahay ga"
19,63,yeh hai woh jannat jis ka waris hum apne bundon mein se uss ko banayen ge jo parhaizgaar raha hai
19,64,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum tumahray rab ke hukum ke baghair nahi utra karte jo kuch hamaray agay hai aur jo kuch peechay hai aur jo kuch is ke darmain hai har cheez ka maalik wohi hai aur tumhara rab bhoolnay wala nahi hai"
